name: Verify user should able to book Pro rata Cancellation type when transaction date is greater than system date

testSteps.description: 1: Verify user should able to book Pro rata Cancellation type when transaction date is greater than system date ({cancellationtype=Pro rata, cancellationreason=Agent of Record})

children.description: Given underwriter has ability to create policy for LOB Workers Compensation
Given user has a WK Policy
When user cancels policy for transaction effective date greater than system date
Then user can able to book Cancellation transaction with cancellation type Pro rata and cancellation reason Agent of Record
And the same is updated in Billing system
